race.comment: DR. MAVERICK (6) recorded a 6 length win in a Maiden last time 24.93 at this track and trip and also jumping from the same draw. Can continue the winning form. JADE'S HOT (1) turned in a moderate effort last time when sixth at this track over 435m behind Dr. Gianna (25.60) in a T3 Grade 7. Expected to run well. PANTS (5) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (25.04) at this track behind Dr. Tessa in a Grade 7. Has the early speed to give a sight. Must be included in calculations. ROCHARD (2) is a last-start placegetter at big odds who will have admirers. Something for the Multiples: DR. MAVERICK (6)
